 Hollywood Actor and Comedian, Michael Blackson’s Girlfriend Miss Rada Has broken up with him. Taking to her official Instagram page Miss Rada disclosed that she is done with the comedian. Posting a picture of herself with Michael Blackson , she wrote: “it has been a great ride…..although I love him to death, he has internal issues that he needs to work on. I am an easy person to deal with but I will not be lied to, I will always love and support him with all my heart……it’s time for me to move on and love him from afar. Enjoy the Gold Coast….my side beeches and I are moving on #takecare”. The couple has been dating for two years as they marked their second anniversary in March, visited Ghana together in January. Michael Blackson is yet to make any comment on this development.